import React from 'react';
import clsx from 'clsx';
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import Checkbox from '@material-ui/core/Checkbox';
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid';
import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button';
import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography';
import { createMuiTheme, ThemeProvider } from '@material-ui/core/styles';

import {
  Container,
  Card,
  CardHeader,
  Divider,
  FormControlLabel,
  makeStyles,
  Box,
} from '@material-ui/core';

const theme = createMuiTheme();

theme.typography.h3 = {
  fontSize: '1.2rem',
  '@media (min-width:600px)': {
    fontSize: '1.5rem',
  },
  [theme.breakpoints.up('md')]: {
    fontSize: '2rem',
  },
};

const useStyles = makeStyles(() => ({
  root: {
    display: 'flex',
    height: '100%',
    with: '100%'
  }
}));

const TrafficByDevice = ({ className, ...rest }) => {
  const classes = useStyles();

  return (
    <Container fixed>
      <Box mb={3} ml={1}>
        <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
          <Typography variant="h3">INBOX</Typography>
        </ThemeProvider>
      </Box>
      <Card className={clsx(classes.root, className)} {...rest}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid className={classes.item} item md={9} sm={9} xs={9}>
            <Grid item md={12} sm={12} xs={12}>
              <Box root md={10} sm={10} xs={10}>
                <CardHeader h2 title="COMPLETED" />
              </Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid className={classes.item} item md={3} sm={3} xs={3}>
            <Box display="flex" mt={1} justifyContent="flex-end">
              <Button variant="outlined" disabled>
                Clear not completed
              </Button>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            {/* <CardHeader h2 title="TODO" /> */}
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={<Checkbox />}
                  label="4517 Washington Ave. Manchester, Kentucky 39495"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={<Checkbox />}
                  label="2715 Ash Dr. San Jose, South Dakota 83475"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={<Checkbox />}
                  label="2118 Thornridge Cir. Syracuse, Connecticut 35624"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={<Checkbox />}
                  label="6391 Elgin St. Celina, Delaware 10299"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid className={classes.item} item md={9} sm={9} xs={9}>
            <Grid item md={12} sm={12} xs={12}>
              <Box root md={10} sm={10} xs={10}>
                <CardHeader h2 title="COMPLETED" />
              </Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid className={classes.item} item md={3} sm={3} xs={3}>
            <Box display="flex" mb={4} justifyContent="flex-end">
              <Button variant="outlined" disabled>
                Clear not completed
              </Button>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={(
                    <Checkbox defaultChecked />
                )}
                  label="4517 Washington Ave. Manchester, Kentucky 39495"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={(
                    <Checkbox defaultChecked />
                )}
                  label="4517 Washington Ave. Manchester, Kentucky 39495"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Box borderBottom={1} display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <Box ml={1} mb={2}>
                <FormControlLabel
                  control={(
                    <Checkbox defaultChecked />
                )}
                  label="4517 Washington Ave. Manchester, Kentucky 39495"
                />
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>

          <Divider />
        </Grid>

      </Card>
    </Container>

  );
};

TrafficByDevice.propTypes = {
  className: PropTypes.string
};

export default TrafficByDevice;
